TwipperO is a Twitter replica, with it's most basic functionality.  TwipperO imports Accounts and Social Frameworks to
authenticate user login through your iPhones Accounts database and enables the user to send Tweets.

It was a challenge to enable rapid tweet load as user scrolls through TwipperO.

Design
The UI is very simple. There is simply one user interaction - send tweets.

App is adaptable adapt to various Apple devices.

This prototype was designed within created in 3hours.
